[Cayman (Shanghai) Group]

277
00:20:59,010 --> 00:21:01,660
Is this all the information on the participants?

278
00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:07,540
Director Fang, do you have to look at all of this information on the participants?

279
00:21:07,540 --> 00:21:08,860
Of course.

280
00:21:08,860 --> 00:21:11,000
But you can also look at it on site.

281
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:14,570
You are a judge, why are you more tired than the participants?

282
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:17,940
Isn't it live?

283
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:20,040
Then I have to say something.

284
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:24,720
Or else, people will think your director is an idiot. Isn't that right?

285
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:27,530
With your qualifications, who would dare do that?

286
00:21:29,810 --> 00:21:32,810
Director Fang, at the opening ceremony of the competition later,

287
00:21:32,810 --> 00:21:35,590
will you get on the same stage as President Tang?

288
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:37,110
Yes.

289
00:21:38,190 --> 00:21:39,550
Don't blame me for speaking too much.

290
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:42,320
Cayman has also invested in this competition.

291
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:46,410
Even though you don't like President Tang, please don't—

292
00:21:47,410 --> 00:21:50,350
I'm afraid of how I would explain it to upper management.

293
00:21:50,350 --> 00:21:51,460
I got it.

294
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:54,480
Do you think your director is that senseless?

295
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:57,890
No, I'm just afraid that you'll have a moment of impulsiveness.

296
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,860
[Mo Fei]

297
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:20,950
- President Tang, I hope we have a pleasant collaboration.
- Thank you for your support, President Zhang.

298
00:22:21,910 --> 00:22:23,460
- President Wu.
- President Tang.

299
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:25,650
I hope to have a pleasant collaboration.

300
00:22:25,650 --> 00:22:27,600
[Mingyuan Fashion - "Chinese Style Fashion"]

301
00:22:28,610 --> 00:22:30,090
Have a seat.

302
00:22:32,030 --> 00:22:36,670
Hello, President Tang. Can you tell us about your thoughts on Chinese Style Fashion?

303
00:22:36,670 --> 00:22:40,740
Mingyuan greatly supports Chinese Style Fashion because

304
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:43,150
we hope to provide young local designers

305
00:22:43,150 --> 00:22:46,730
a platform to showcase their talent.

306
00:22:46,730 --> 00:22:49,070
All right. Thank you, President Tang.

307
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:51,770
Hello, President Wu, are there any thoughts

308
00:22:51,770 --> 00:22:53,690
you would like to share about the

309
00:22:53,690 --> 00:22:56,020
Chinese Style Fashion event that Mingyuan is hosting?

310
00:22:56,020 --> 00:22:58,530
As an online sales platform,

311
00:22:58,530 --> 00:23:02,440
our Fashion Daily is mainly focused on designers with

312
00:23:02,440 --> 00:23:05,870
the greatest potential emerging from Chinese Style Fashion.

313
00:23:05,870 --> 00:23:09,950
We want to provide them with an exclusive online selling platform

314
00:23:09,950 --> 00:23:13,480
and give them many opportunities to diversify development even more. Thank you.

315
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:16,860
Then, Director Fang, what are your thoughts?

316
00:23:17,330 --> 00:23:19,340
Are you asking me?

317
00:23:19,340 --> 00:23:22,690
I'm a designer, so, of course, I would support creative competitions.

318
00:23:22,690 --> 00:23:24,570
However, in the current industry,

319
00:23:24,570 --> 00:23:27,750
it's a bit impetuous and there are too many people who just want to make money.

320
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:29,890
There are too few who truly want to create designs.

321
00:23:29,890 --> 00:23:32,530
So some companies use this kind of event as a gimmick

322
00:23:32,530 --> 00:23:34,730
to generate interest.

323
00:23:34,730 --> 00:23:38,350
I just didn’t expect that some companies would do something like this.

324
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:44,060
I must say a few words.

325
00:23:44,780 --> 00:23:47,900
Currently, international brands

326
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:51,760
occupy more than half of our domestic fashion market.

327
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:54,250
Think about what our domestic brands

328
00:23:54,250 --> 00:23:57,680
have become because they are not able to make a living.

329
00:23:57,680 --> 00:24:01,150
Become manufacturers instead? Isn't that ridiculous?

330
00:24:01,150 --> 00:24:03,920
If an event like this

331
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:06,120
can give our domestic brands

332
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:08,520
an opportunity to become popular,

333
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:12,370
then won't that have a positive effect?

334
00:24:13,030 --> 00:24:15,630
Our Cayman's style has always been clear.

335
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:18,340
We keep a low profile and we have our own limit.

336
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:20,850
Our Cayman has tens of thousands of ways to be popular.

337
00:24:20,850 --> 00:24:23,900
It doesn't have to be through these means which President Tang speaks about, right?

338
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:26,790
Director Fang, l-let me explain this.

339
00:24:26,790 --> 00:24:29,720
Actually, the industry and media have come together for this competition

340
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,470
because our main goal is

341
00:24:31,470 --> 00:24:33,280
that through Chinese Style Fashion, we can find—

342
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:35,290
President Wu.

343
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:38,160
You are being too serious.

344
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:41,910
Let me tell you. Director Fang likes to be humorous.

345
00:24:41,910 --> 00:24:44,060
Say, if we all haven't come to an agreement,

346
00:24:44,060 --> 00:24:46,630
then would we all be sitting here at the same table?

347
00:24:46,630 --> 00:24:49,630
- You all must report this positively.
- That's right.

348
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:53,820
So, in any industry, there must be a company that can turn the tide.

349
00:24:53,820 --> 00:24:56,850
That is the reason why I'm representing Cayman here.

350
00:24:56,850 --> 00:24:59,740
- Let's give Cayman a round of applause.
- All right.

351
00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:09,360
Hurry up and have a seat.

352
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:12,370
Director Fang, why did ask me to come here in such a hurry?

353
00:25:12,370 --> 00:25:14,140
Don't be worried. What would you like to drink?

354
00:25:14,140 --> 00:25:15,860
I'll just have water. Thank you.

355
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:18,740
Waiter, a glass of water, please.

356
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:22,520
The Chinese Style competition is going to start soon.

357
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:25,010
How is your design going?

358
00:25:25,580 --> 00:25:29,690
Why are the judges in such a hurry to start giving scores?

359
00:25:29,690 --> 00:25:31,190
Why are you so serious?

360
00:25:31,190 --> 00:25:32,990
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

361
00:25:32,990 --> 00:25:37,870
I am a judge, so, of course, I'm interested in the contestants' works.

362
00:25:38,490 --> 00:25:41,250
Also, I do have selfish motives.

363
00:25:41,250 --> 00:25:45,260
The winner of this competition can sign with our Cayman.

364
00:25:45,260 --> 00:25:49,010
I want to train a capable assistant for myself.

365
00:25:52,180 --> 00:25:57,270
So, is this you secretly opening the back door for me?

366
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:01,610
What? Do you not want to join Cayman?

367
00:26:01,610 --> 00:26:04,190
That's not what I mean, I just think...

368
00:26:04,190 --> 00:26:06,450
Since you are a judge, you should

369
00:26:06,450 --> 00:26:10,590
be fair to each competitor.

370
00:26:11,450 --> 00:26:13,340
Do you think that our Cayman

371
00:26:13,340 --> 00:26:16,000
opens back doors for anyone randomly?

372
00:26:17,050 --> 00:26:19,260
I am doing it

373
00:26:19,260 --> 00:26:21,480
because I cherish and love talent.

374
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:24,300
Because I understand and admire your work,

375
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:26,940
as well as recognize your capabilites.

376
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:29,340
How can you reject me so fast?

377
00:26:29,340 --> 00:26:31,980
I'm just being honest.

378
00:26:31,980 --> 00:26:34,820
Don't take it to heart, but thank you!

379
00:26:34,820 --> 00:26:36,740
For thinking of me when it comes to good opportunities.

380
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,770
Since you're so honest, I can't honestly be mad at you.

381
00:26:38,770 --> 00:26:42,050
If there is nothing else, I am leaving. I still have things to do.

382
00:26:42,050 --> 00:26:44,480
Not so fast. How about I give you a ride?

383
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:46,610
It's fine. It's related to the competition anyway.

384
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:48,770
I have already made plans to film with my friend.

385
00:26:48,770 --> 00:26:50,820
So, I need to go.

386
00:26:50,820 --> 00:26:52,550
What are you shooting? Tell me.

387
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:56,990
Just some preparation work for before the competition starts, like choosing fabric.

388
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:58,920
You are a designer.

389
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:02,190
Going there like this, wouldn't you be dressed too casually?

390
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:04,040
Have a seat first and wait a moment for me.

391
00:27:04,040 --> 00:27:06,080
- But—
- Sit.

392
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:08,450
Waiter, can you bring me scissors? Thank you.

393
00:27:08,450 --> 00:27:12,000
- I'm really in a hurry.
- It'll be really quick.

394
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:42,230
Let me borrow that pin of yours.

395
00:28:05,050 --> 00:28:07,010
Wear it on your chest.

396
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,730
Thank you, Director Fang.

397
00:28:15,810 --> 00:28:18,990
Perfect. A unique flower

398
00:28:18,990 --> 00:28:21,910
for a unique designer.

399
00:28:21,910 --> 00:28:24,160
I have high expectations from you. Don't disappoint me.

400
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:26,050
Thank you.

401
00:28:26,820 --> 00:28:29,750
I'm already late. I really need to go. Thank you.

402
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:31,860
I will definitely do my best in the competition.

403
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:33,700
- I can do it!
- You can do it!

404
00:28:33,700 --> 00:28:35,350
- Bye-bye!
- You can do it!

405
00:28:35,350 --> 00:28:37,260
- I can do it!
- Yes!

406
00:28:45,910 --> 00:28:49,380
Please look forward to my oceanic tung flower. Thank you.

407
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:51,440
- Was that all right?
- Yes.

408
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:54,100
When will the next person be here?

409
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:56,890
I'm sorry. Can you wait a bit longer?

410
00:28:56,890 --> 00:28:59,000
I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

411
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:14,590
My lord, you're finally here!

412
00:29:14,590 --> 00:29:17,680
I'm sorry, so sorry. Did you finish filming?

413
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:20,940
I have finished a long time ago. If I didn't beg that director sister, they would have left long ago.

414
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:23,540
- T-Then I'll go apologize right away.
- Wait, Sis.

415
00:29:23,540 --> 00:29:25,860
Are you doing your greeting on-screen like this?

416
00:29:25,860 --> 00:29:28,400
This is your on-screen debut!

417
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,810
W-Wait.

418
00:29:30,810 --> 00:29:33,760
H-Help me hold this.

419
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:35,890
D-Don't move!

420
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:48,330
Will this do? Okay. Let's go.

421
00:29:56,550 --> 00:29:58,790
I'm sorry, so sorry.

422
00:30:27,190 --> 00:30:28,570
Boss, please.

423
00:30:28,570 --> 00:30:31,530
- All right, how do you want it cut?
- The usual way.

424
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:41,160
Okay. Cut!

425
00:30:42,050 --> 00:30:43,990
Boss, thank you so much.

426
00:30:43,990 --> 00:30:45,910
- I've troubled you.
- Not at all.

427
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:48,520
No trouble at all!

428
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:51,710
I can't believe an old geezer like me can actually be on TV.

429
00:30:53,090 --> 00:30:55,920
Which channel is it? Tell me when it airs.

430
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:57,620
I am going to tell my son to watch it.

431
00:30:57,620 --> 00:31:01,230
- Don't worry, when it airs I will definitely inform you.
- Okay.

432
00:31:01,230 --> 00:31:04,680
Mo Fei. In a bit, look at the screen and explain why you chose the fabric.

433
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:07,070
Then we're done, all right?

434
00:31:14,350 --> 00:31:18,260
When I received the theme of "misty rain in Jiangnan," I thought,

435
00:31:18,260 --> 00:31:21,150
"What is a special characteristic of Jiangnan?"

436
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:24,430
I think it should be Jiangnan's water.

437
00:31:24,430 --> 00:31:27,030
Jiangnan's water is the gentlest.

438
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:30,100
So for the fabric this time, I chose silk.

439
00:31:30,100 --> 00:31:32,640
And what color should Jiangnan's water be?

440
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:35,290
I thought of a poem about Jiangnan.

441
00:31:35,290 --> 00:31:38,910
"Spring water as blue as the sky. Laying in a beautifully decorated boat, falling asleep to the sound of the rain."

442
00:31:38,910 --> 00:31:42,410
The color of a clear sky after rain in Jiangnan should be the most beautiful.

443
00:31:42,410 --> 00:31:45,260
This is why the main color I chose for my design

444
00:31:45,260 --> 00:31:47,090
is cerulean blue.

445
00:31:47,090 --> 00:31:49,180
Okay. Cut! This is great.

446
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:52,200
That's it for today. We are done.

447
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:55,200
- Thank you so much.
- Mo Fei.

448
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:58,570
Since the fabric has been chosen, what is the next step for you contestants?

449
00:31:58,570 --> 00:32:01,750
Next, we will go to Mingyuan's design studio to make the designs.

450
00:32:01,750 --> 00:32:04,320
Mingyuan has provided us an especially professional space to work.

451
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:07,970
Then Director Sister, will you guys be coming with us to film?

452
00:32:07,970 --> 00:32:11,330
No. To go into Mingyuan's design studio, you need to sign a confidentiality agreement.

453
00:32:11,330 --> 00:32:13,880
Also, you need to keep confidential until the designs are finished and made.

454
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:16,360
Then that is great! We can finally breathe.

455
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:18,730
Thank you so much today.

456
00:32:21,650 --> 00:32:24,960
Today was so exhausting! My back!

457
00:32:25,670 --> 00:32:28,660
But, Mo Fei, you did so well!

458
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:31,200
When you hurried over, I was afraid you might make some mistake.

459
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:34,170
But I can't believe once you went on camera, you immediately spoke with confidence and fluency.

460
00:32:34,170 --> 00:32:37,440
You didn't see, but that Director Sister immediately went from gloomy to sunny.

461
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:40,780
Let me tell you! I was so nervous that I was shaking.

462
00:32:40,780 --> 00:32:44,560
I feel, that once this airs, you'll definitely become popular.

463
00:32:44,560 --> 00:32:47,820
Once you are famous, how are you going to thank me?

464
00:32:49,950 --> 00:32:52,340
I'll treat you to delicious food.

465
00:32:52,340 --> 00:32:54,610
Like what?

466
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:56,440
Hotpot!

467
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,070
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

468
00:32:58,070 --> 00:32:59,680
Let's go.

469
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:17,140
You're here again?

470
00:33:25,370 --> 00:33:28,480
[Mingyuan Fashion Group, Mo Fei, Designer]

471
00:33:33,980 --> 00:33:35,800
Please.

472
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:03,480
- Why are you—
- Why are you—

473
00:34:06,390 --> 00:34:08,570
Why are you here?

474
00:34:09,410 --> 00:34:12,610
I think I'm on the wrong floor. I need to go to the design studio.

475
00:34:12,610 --> 00:34:15,820
This whole floor is my office yet you're looking for the design studio here?

476
00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:18,820
- It's downstairs.
- Okay, I'll get going.
- No, wait.

477
00:34:18,820 --> 00:34:22,060
I happen to need to talk to you. Let's go to my office.

478
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:22,990
Let me help you.

479
00:34:22,990 --> 00:34:24,850
I can carry it myself.

480
00:34:24,850 --> 00:34:29,040
You don't know yet, right? This company's boss particularly likes to

481
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:32,310
deduct the employees' bonuses.

482
00:34:32,310 --> 00:34:34,890
Since we know each other so well, I can't get you in trouble. Right?

483
00:34:34,890 --> 00:34:39,360
If we run into the boss, then your wallet would be wronged. Right?

484
00:34:41,550 --> 00:34:43,270
Come on.

485
00:34:46,400 --> 00:34:48,330
Is this for me?

486
00:34:48,330 --> 00:34:51,850
Though Master Li's small courtyard is complete, I think it's still missing a lot of things.

487
00:34:51,850 --> 00:34:54,540
I had the purchasing department make a list.

488
00:34:54,540 --> 00:34:58,070
They don’t know much about embroidery, so please review it for me.

489
00:34:58,070 --> 00:35:00,680
I think it's too much.

490
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:04,200
I plan to expand the garden a bit more.

491
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:09,350
Your company has too much money, doesn't it?

492
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:15,040
Oh, you have a guest?

493
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:17,470
Xueling, you've met before.

494
00:35:17,470 --> 00:35:20,510
Master Li's disciple, Mo Fei.

495
00:35:21,570 --> 00:35:24,590
- Hello, Miss Mo Fei. We meet again.
- Hello.

496
00:35:27,750 --> 00:35:29,390
Are you all done here?

497
00:35:29,390 --> 00:35:31,740
The new season's designs are almost ready.

498
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:33,560
Do you want to go look at them with me?

499
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:34,790
All right.

500
00:35:34,790 --> 00:35:37,730
Since you're busy, I'll get going first.

501
00:35:37,730 --> 00:35:40,020
Do you want to come with us?

502
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:41,900
Me? Can I?

503
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:44,650
If you are with me, of course you can.
- Okay.

504
00:35:45,230 --> 00:35:46,960
Let's go.

505
00:35:55,570 --> 00:35:57,500
Director Xia.

506
00:36:00,510 --> 00:36:02,320
You! Stop, stop, stop.

507
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,820
Which department are you from?

