00:36:03,820 --> 00:36:07,200
The design studio is currently strictly confidential. Outsiders can't come in.

509
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:08,800
- I brought her here.
- Oh, okay.

510
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:11,230
Let's come in and take a look.

511
00:36:11,230 --> 00:36:12,400
President Tang! President Tang!

512
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:14,290
President Tang!

513
00:36:16,790 --> 00:36:18,330
What's the matter?

514
00:36:18,330 --> 00:36:20,200
It's not appropriate for me to go in.

515
00:36:20,200 --> 00:36:21,850
What's not appropriate about it?

516
00:36:21,850 --> 00:36:22,820
I'm not—

517
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:26,390
Doesn't the badge you wear say that you're Mingyuan Group's designer?

518
00:36:26,390 --> 00:36:28,620
That is what the badge says

519
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:30,960
but I'm just here to participate in the competition.

520
00:36:30,960 --> 00:36:33,780
When we were visiting stores in Suzhou, didn't you do quite well?

521
00:36:33,780 --> 00:36:37,340
In a bit, just say and do what you must. Be poised and confident.

522
00:36:37,340 --> 00:36:40,450
Can that be the same? You have designers here. Won't I offend people in my industry?

523
00:36:40,450 --> 00:36:44,030
Do well and I'll double the pay.

524
00:37:17,420 --> 00:37:19,130
Mo Fei.

525
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:22,190
Tell me. What do you think?

526
00:37:23,410 --> 00:37:26,390
I think it looks great, however I think it's lacking

527
00:37:26,390 --> 00:37:29,880
a bit of the brand's personal cultural characteristics.

528
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,830
Miss Mo.

529
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:35,270
You are being vague.

530
00:37:35,270 --> 00:37:37,880
What do you think is the actual problem?

531
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:42,130
Take this shirt as an example.

532
00:37:42,130 --> 00:37:46,260
Professional style, concise, and capable. The texture is also great.

533
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:50,690
But it's too similar to the 2015 Armani's spring and summer collection.

534
00:37:50,690 --> 00:37:53,490
Even the shape is the same.

535
00:38:02,110 --> 00:38:04,420
And this other one.

536
00:38:05,910 --> 00:38:09,280
It uses the Chinese design of an overlapping collar.

537
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:13,190
The collar and skirt also have Chinese elements.

538
00:38:13,190 --> 00:38:17,430
It's just that it's very similar to Versace's design

539
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:21,480
released in 2019 in Milan.

540
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:23,980
Even the bowknot

541
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:26,870
is very similar.

542
00:38:28,890 --> 00:38:31,420
Miss Mo, you are indeed impressive.

543
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:35,100
