551
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:00,860
What?

552
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:02,870
It's a coincidence.

553
00:39:06,170 --> 00:39:09,290
As a professional designer,

554
00:39:09,290 --> 00:39:12,280
